Package: BiocHubQuery
Type: Package
Title: Functions to query Bioconductor AnnotationHub or ExperimentHub Remotely
Version: 0.99.0
Description: This package reads remote parquet files that are processed from Bioconductor Hub sqlite files. Users may query the tables directly for specific information or use pre-defined helper functions for common queries. This avoids downloading the full hub metadata sqlite file in order to query resources available.
Depends: R (>= 4.6.0)
Imports: arrow, dplyr
